<HEAD>
<TITLE>The Borneo Project: Join Us!</TITLE></HEAD>

<BODY BGCOLOR="FFFBC0" TEXT="800000">

<CENTER> 
<H2>Join Us!</H2> </CENTER>

<BR>

<P>The Borneo Project is a volunteer-based and volunteer-run
organization with more than five years dedicated to indigenous rights and rainforest protection in Borneo. We invite you to join us. Come to one of our monthly committee meetings. Sponsor a slide show in your classroom or office. Share your skills and resources. Or, make a
tax-deductible contribution to one of the many important projects currently under way. </P>

<P>If we are to save Borneo's last remaining stands of virgin rainforest, we must continue to stand behind the rightful stewards of the land.  Your donations to the Borneo Project will help realize more legal victories, support our ongoing projects and catalyze global awareness about the threats to the Sarawak's last remaining forests.  Please help us keep the spirit of citizen diplomacy alive! 



<HR>


</P>
Borneo Project
<BR>  1137 Hearst Ave. #D
<BR>  Berkeley, CA
94702
<BR>  Tel: 510-528-0421
<BR>  Fax: 510-527-7665
<BR>  Email us at: 
<A HREF= "mailto: mbelcher@igc.apc.org">mbelcher@igc.apc.org</A> </P>

