For general Black Mesa information: Big Mountain Support Group, PO Box
26195, Tucson, AZ 85726; (520) 629-9122. For information on the Black Mesa Permaculture
Project: Justin Willy, PO Box 5350, Leupp, AZ 86035. 

The Dine Alliance [PO Box 810, Pinon, AZ 86510; fax: (520) 749-0587; email: dineh @primenet. com] needs tax-deductible contributions
for legal costs and donations of office supplies, IBM-compatible computers and software, solar
panels, a cellular phone and a sturdy truck.  Write checks to Don't Waste America (please write
"for Black Mesa Legal Fund" on  the memo portion of the check), 6205 S. 12th Street, Phoenix, AZ
85040.
