<LI>Ask restaurants and foodstores to carry Turtle-Safe shrimp<P>
<LI>Promote the campaign at public events<P>
<LI>And lots more!<P>
</UL>
<A HREF="mailto:sea turtle@igc.apc.orgs">Contact STRP</A> at 415-488-0370 to receive a Sea Turtle Activist Kit, order copies of our videos and campaign materials, or just to share ideas and strategies.

Thanks for helping us help the sea turtles!


