<TITLE>EINS: Other Organizations and Web sites</TITLE> 
<H1>Other Web Sites</H1>

<A HREF="http://www.igc.apc.org"><IMG SRC="at.igc.gif" Border=0 ALIGN=RIGHT></A>

Did you try to <A HREF="/scripts/wwwwais/config=ei">search</A> our pages? What
your looking for may be in the <A
HREF="../journal/journal.html">Journal</A>. May we also strongly recommend <A HREF="http://www.igc.apc.org/">The Progressive Directory @IGC</A>.<P>

<P>

<HR>
These home pages and organizations are not directly related to EII and some organizations do not have Internet addresses.<P>
This growing list was designed so that viewers can, using most Browsers, search for key words such as "human rights", "Green Plans", or "environmental justice" to locate a particular listing.<P>
<LI>Organizations <A HREF="otherweb.html#wwwgrp">with WWW sites</A> working to protect the Earth<P>
<LI>Organizations <A HREF="otherweb.html#nowwwgrp">without WWW sites</A> working to protect the Earth<P>
