tel: (33 for France) 78 36 93 03<BR>
fax: (33 for France) 78 36 26 83<BR>
email: cdrpc@gn.apc.org<BR>
Works on peace and national security issues. Operates an Observatory of Arms Transfers, which centers in a database on the French nuclear weapons industry and transfers of France with a 9600 baud modem and videotext emulator.  To the Observatory publishes La Lettre de l'Observatoire in English and French.<P>

Mineral Policy Center<BR>
