<H1>The Brower Fund</H1>



<IMG SRC="brower.jpg"

ALIGN=RIGHT

HEIGHT=190 WIDTH=180>



The Brower Fund supports innovative approaches to environmental conservation, 

protection, and restoration.  The Brower Fund makes small grants to start new and critical 

environmental initiatives, both within Earth Island and within other organizations.  The Fund 

also incubates some of David Brower's most urgent projects.  In 1993 David Brower 

embarked upon his <CITE>Vision for Action</CITE> speaking tour of the United States and 

Europe giving speeches, participating in conferences, and talking to the press about the 

state of the environment.  Project Director: David Brower.<P>



See also <A HREF="browerbr.html">David Brower's Browser</A>



