<title>Background Information Kenya</title>



</head>







<body>







<H2>Background information on Kenya and GSC's Kenya Projects</H2>







<UL>



<LI><B><A HREF="manor.html">Training by Collaboration</A></B> 



by Lincolin Ornston. The report of an ex-volunteer of his stay in Kenya.



<LI><B><A HREF="kres.html">Kenya resources</A></B> on the Internet.



</UL><p>







<HR>







<UL>



<LI>Other trips: <A HREF="costa.html">Costa Rica Eco-Service Project</A> | 



