<H2>From Earth Island's Executive Directors<BR>John A. Knox & David Phillips</H2>







When Earth Island Institute became a membership organization in 1986, neither of us 



imagined what a growing and vibrant network of projects would evolve.  Our 



successes owe a great deal to our unique structure. Our core staff researches emerging



issues and educates the public about effective action.  We nurture the development 



of projects to address these issues, and provide a support structure within which 



projects can concentrate on content rather than administration and get the job done.<P>



















