House Office Building<BR>
Washington, DC 20515</BLOCKQUOTE><P>

<BLOCKQUOTE>Capitol: (202) 224-3121</BLOCKQUOTE></LI>

<LI>Write to Vice President Al Gore and urge that, due to Norway's defiance of the IWC, the US administration place sanctions on Norway's fish products.  It is time for the US government to get tough!<P>

<BLOCKQUOTE>The White House<BR>
1600 Pennsylvania Ave., NW<BR>
Washington, DC 20500</BLOCKQUOTE></LI>

<LI>Write to Gro Harlem Bruntland, Prime Minister of Norway. Demand that Norway put an end to the senseless slaughter of whales.<P>

<BLOCKQUOTE>Gro Harlem Bruntland, P.M.<BR>
Norwegian Embassy<BR>
2720 34th St., NW<BR>
Washington, DC 20008</BLOCKQUOTE></LI>

<LI>Don't buy Norwegian products, such as fish and cheese, until Norway stops whaling.</LI>

<LI>Urge local supermarkets not to sell Norwegian products.</LI>

</UL>

