	Scripps Institute of Oceanography<BR>
	8604 La Jolla Shores Drive<BR>
	La Jolla, CA  92037
<P>

<LI>Write to the National Marine Fisheries Service (NMFS). Demand that it opposes 
efforts to weaken all marine mammal protection laws.<BR>
	Dr. William Fox<BR>
	NMFS<BR>
	1335 E. West Highway<BR>
	Silver Springs, MD  20910
</UL>
