<H1>IMMP: What you can do</H1>
<TITLE>What you can do</TITLE>
<I>The Winter/Spring 1995 Ocean Alert (formerly the Dolphin Alert) is an Earth Island Institute publication.</I><P>

<H2>Take Action</H2>

<UL>

<LI>Don't buy any tuna unless it is approved dolphin-safe by Earth 
Island Institute.<P>

<LI>Don't buy Norwegian products, such as fish and cheese, until 
Norway stops whaling.<P>

<LI>Urge local supermarkets and restaurants to sell only EII approved, dolphin-safe tuna and not to sell Norwegian products.<P>

<LI>Ensure that your school cafeteria or workplace serves only EII 
approved, dolphin-safe tuna.<P>

<LI>Sponsor a dolphin species and help  protect it in the wild. <P>

</UL>

<H2>Inform the Public </H2>
<UL>

<LI>Create school units that focus on  dolphins, whales, and the marine ecosystem. Write to us if you would like the Life in the Sea Discovery Kit. Please include $3.00 for shipping.<P>

<LI>Set up "dolphin and whale" booths at supermarkets, fairs, and other events.  Distribute our literature and inform people about the dolphin and whale slaughter.<P>

<LI>Host a video party for your family and friends.  Show the dramatic video Where Have All the Dolphins Gone?  and hand out  IMMP's literature.
  
<LI>Start an environmental club at your school. Organize local citizen action groups. Get involved! <P>
</UL>

<H2>Voice Your Opinion</H2>
<UL>

<LI>Encourage local newspapers, 
radio, and TV stations to cover the tuna/dolphin and whaling issues.<P>

<LI>Write articles for your school newspapers or business publications to educate others about the tuna/dolphin and whaling issues.<P>

<LI>Send letters to your senators and representatives encouraging them to take a strong position against commercial whaling. <P>


<LI>Write letters to the editor of your local newspapers and express your concern for marine mammals.<P>

<LI>Encourage your senators and representatives to uphold the IDCA. Tell them not to let it be repealed or amended in a way that would weaken its provisions. <P>
</UL>
<H2>Write Letters</H2>
<UL>
<LI>Write to Pres. Clinton and VP  Gore. Demand that Clinton place sanctions on Norway until it stops commercial whaling. <P>
The White House<BR>
