<HTML>
<HEAD>
<TITLE>The Borneo Project: Borneo Proclimation</TITLE></HEAD>

<BODY BGCOLOR="FFFBC0" TEXT="800000">

<IMG
ALIGN="BOTTOM" SRC="berk-proclimation.gif" ALT="Borneo Proclimation"> 

<CENTER>
<H2>Greeetings to the People of Uma Bawang</H2></CENTER>

<P>WHEREAS,on behalf of the city of Berkeley, California, I hereby extend my
greetings and warm welcom to the people of Uma Bawang; and  
</P> 

<P>WHEREAS, both Berkeley and Uma Bawang are concerned about the preservation
of the environment and the well-being of future generations; and</P>

<P>WHEREAS, both communities share common goals of educating our children and
providing for all community members to the best of our ability; and</P>

<P>WHEREAS, both communities would benefit from exchanges of information, goods
and cultural values, since the people of both Uma Bawang and Berkeley recognize
the increasing interdependence of all peoples with each other and with nature;
and</P>

<P>WHEREAS, the people of Uma Bawang have expressed strong interest in forming
a sister city relationship with Berkeley; and</P>

<P>WHEREAS, Berkeley citizens on the Big Home Project have expressed similar
interest in establishing ties with the people of Uma Bawang.</P>

<P>NOW, THEREFORE, BE IT RESOLVED, that, I, Lori Hancock, Mayor of the City of
Berkeley, do hereby authorize the Borneo Project to explore the
possibility of forming a sister city relationship with the people of Uma Bawang
through which our two communities can form ties of mutual friendship and
support.</P>


<HR>

