<UL>

<LI>1) Tropical log import figures prior to 1995 do not include imports from Africa.  
<P>

<LI>2) Figures given for 1995 tropical sawnwood imports are totals for Jan. - Nov. U95 from Nihon Nanyozai Kyogikai (Japan South Seas Timber Council) Jan. U96 Statistics.  Figures for other years are for the full year and are from Nikkan Mokuzai Shimbun.  

