      phone (310) 399-TREE; fax (310) 399-5303.
      <LI><B>Tree Free Eco-Paper</B>: Sells hemp and agri-residue paper. (800)
      775-0225 (OR).
      <LI><B>Hempstead</B>: Sells a variety of hemp products. 2060 Placentia
      B-2, Costa Mesa, CA 92627. Phone (800) 284-HEMP; fax (714) 650-5853.
      <LI><B>Earth Care Products</B>, 555 Leslie St., Ukiah CA 95482: Sells kenaf
      supplies for home and office. See website at http://www.realgoods.com/.
      Email: <A HREF="mailto:realgoods@relgoods.com">realgoods@realgoods.com</A>.
      Sells hemp paper and 100% recycled office paper. Phone 1-800- 347-0070.
      <LI><B>Ohio Hempery</B>: Offers hemp papers and products. (800) BUY-HEMP
      (OH).
      <LI><B>Ecolution</B>: Sells hemp paper and products. 2800 Juniper St.,
      Suite 2, Fairfax, VA 22031; phone (703) 207-9001; fax (703) 560-1175.
      <LI><B>Arbour</B>: Sells a selection of hemp paper. (613) 567-3168 (Ontario,
      Canada).
    </UL>
  </BLOCKQUOTE>
  <P>&nbsp;</P>
