<H2>GLOBAL SERVICE CORPS NEWSLETTER (PRINTED EDITION)</H2>







The Global Service Corps Newsletter is published quarterly and includes



the following information:<p> 







<UL>



<LI>Description of upcoming projects trips



<LI>Schedule and cost of upcoming project trips



<LI>Latest news of the development projects, our host organizations and GSC volunteers and staff



<LI>Registration information for project trips



</UL><p>







<I>The newsletter is provided free of charge.  To subscribe, forward the your name, address and phone



number to Global Service Corps Volunteers, 300 Broadway Ave., Suite 39, San Francisco, CA 94133-3312, 



USA.  



Or E-mail us at <A HREF="mailto:gsc@igc.apc.org">gsc@igc.apc.org</A>.</I>







